406d3848df9c0291362399795c30","tid":382884,"uid":83602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一"},{"pid":"961151e7840ec4df977da651d2eaf13f4537c258","tid":382884,"uid":31894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火影世界第一</blockquote><br />\n無動漫超越到火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6915fbf11c1ce96430beb21fe44998db65db3d68","tid":382884,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"海狗王咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2ca86703a31bb69c09a322414d18fa47d73662","tid":382884,"uid":118250,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時讀中學d fd係咁叫我睇op<br />\n又話好撚正好熱血好好睇<br />\n仲拎埋d銷量呀排名呀出黎吹捧op世界第一<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日個個睇到屌哂鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連曾經被譽為世界第一<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">垃圾</span></span>既火影都比下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係晚節不保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利 冇睇過op 火影睇到一半頂唔順"},{"pid":"c256e824e94217f25c389edee14d6fe983930878","tid":382884,"uid":31894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:12:29.000Z","msg":"睇黎火影完美KO海賊王"},{"pid":"938976fdf5b7d8522954a1a51d9da578774b90cd","tid":382884,"uid":2588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"以前火影未完就屌到開花 <br />\n火影一完就已經係連登上咗神枱啦使乜再開呢啲post"},{"pid":"077c471dfaf3de89ebe25fccaaadf72ad6f8d3f9","tid":382884,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"動畫就one piece<br />\n漫畫就火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb5bcf1304e089342d6c222231150525170636b","tid":382884,"uid":86587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:40:03.000Z","msg":"路遙知馬力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年睇火影就覺得啲人踩得太犀利，海賊王比人捧得太過份。佐助打鼬又話幻術對幻術太誇張。打佩恩又話主角威能。根本呢部份就火影最好睇個part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相反海賊王啲戰鬥先係又亂又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n就算係忍界大戰都無想像中咁爛，睇宇智波斑屈人機都唔知幾爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最起碼都好過兩年後既海賊王，除咗羅之外毫無亮點"},{"pid":"131fa93d4f6aba115ab7e2eb31d1b5cb243a213e","tid":382884,"uid":94757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路遙知馬力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年睇火影就覺得啲人踩得太犀利，海賊王比人捧得太過份。佐助打鼬又話幻術對幻術太誇張。打佩恩又話主角威能。根本呢部份就火影最好睇個part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相反海賊王啲戰鬥先係又亂又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n就算係忍界大戰都無想像中咁爛，睇宇智波斑屈人機都唔知幾爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最起碼都好過兩年後既海賊王，除咗羅之外毫無亮點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忍界大戰一開始我覺得好悶 打埋晒咩金角銀角 舊影同少年篇D角色<br />\n去到之後得番班同帶土就好睇番好多 同埋大筒木既故事都唔錯<br />\n個尾都叫收得好冇點再拖"},{"pid":"80b20cb7506166ca3f46a8a875319b747544136c","tid":382884,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"當年由佐助打迪達拉開始到完忍界大戰<br />\n都被人屌3秒睇完屌到上天花板<br />\n<br />\n依加上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOp真係要完左先有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8974731d415f98a0392c78ec48a5164a90e8cec0","tid":382884,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>路遙知馬力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年睇火影就覺得啲人踩得太犀利，海賊王比人捧得太過份。佐助打鼬又話幻術對幻術太誇張。打佩恩又話主角威能。根本呢部份就火影最好睇個part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相反海賊王啲戰鬥先係又亂又悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n就算係忍界大戰都無想像中咁爛，睇宇智波斑屈人機都唔知幾爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最起碼都好過兩年後既海賊王，除咗羅之外毫無亮點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">忍界大戰一開始我覺得好悶 打埋晒咩金角銀角 舊影同少年篇D角色<br />\n</span>去到之後得番班同帶土就好睇番好多 同埋大筒木既故事都唔錯<br />\n個尾都叫收得好冇點再拖</blockquote><br />\n不能再同意更多，次次翻睇都直接飛到斑復活個度開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cc5230b61cc3ca7900cce2cd08bd227f0f0ede","tid":382884,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年由佐助打迪達拉開始到完忍界大戰<br />\n都被人屌3秒睇完屌到上天花板<br />\n<br />\n依加上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOp真係要完左先有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我14年先一次過睇火影同海賊王，個陣火影先做到斑比黑絕背刺。個陣已經覺得火影係戰鬥，節奏同感人位做得好過海賊王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以今日評價變成咁樣完全唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b267bff7e3d5ce683e838bf0df1809c0692e0b3a","tid":382884,"uid":115607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"海柒王人物造型 打鬥 畫風都輸火影幾條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路飛一路以來都無成長過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鳩叫鳩喊就當熱血當感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔係用劇情發展去表達個種情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 故事套路仲要咁公式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5b4be5704280c9b0489f001d26a9e1506d59b7","tid":382884,"uid":31894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海柒王人物造型 打鬥 畫風都輸火影幾條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路飛一路以來都無成長過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鳩叫鳩喊就當熱血當感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔係用劇情發展去表達個種情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 故事套路仲要咁公式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意路飛好似一直以來都無成長過咁<br />\n成個傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火影內心描寫做得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cbea44fd6ba77022c72fdc27c90ed96e92519c","tid":382884,"uid":40318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"火影係平均垃圾 海賊cp9精彩 打完cp9後話佢垃圾都侮辱緊垃圾 <br />\n兩年後直情當佢無再出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a611eefc49c1550dc7eee9c27c95f3ed8cad9d","tid":382884,"uid":89677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火影係平均垃圾 海賊cp9精彩 打完cp9後話佢垃圾都侮辱緊垃圾 <br />\n兩年後直情當佢無再出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踩到咁  其實你呢料呢？"},{"pid":"b25ef9c15060e540a449d44d1990f17210a9effa","tid":382884,"uid":89677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>火影係平均垃圾 海賊cp9精彩 打完cp9後話佢垃圾都侮辱緊垃圾 <br />\n兩年後直情當佢無再出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踩到咁  其實你咩料呢？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1e5db99615fc2e793e44b10f90fa1e32d07d40e9","tid":382884,"uid":31894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火影係平均垃圾 海賊cp9精彩 打完cp9後話佢垃圾都侮辱緊垃圾 <br />\n兩年後直情當佢無再出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩年後無啦啦強行加霸氣呢個設定入黎<br />\n搞到好似變左兩套野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6faa081b95fc8ac0e4fff95a4fd95b96b9cab2","tid":382884,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>火影係平均垃圾 海賊cp9精彩 打完cp9後話佢垃圾都侮辱緊垃圾 <br />\n兩年後直情當佢無再出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踩到咁  其實你咩料呢？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"33675d36ba35916ba0700d499195f586fc2f6071","tid":382884,"uid":79672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海柒王人物造型 打鬥 畫風都輸火影幾條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路飛一路以來都無成長過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鳩叫鳩喊就當熱血當感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔係用劇情發展去表達個種情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 故事套路仲要咁公式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意路飛好似一直以來都無成長過咁<br />\n成個傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火影內心描寫做得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過左咁多年,經歷咁多大事,路飛一點成長都無重係on99<br />\n唔係拎住雞脾行黎行去就大叫我要做海賊王<br />\n其他成員都唔見得好去邊<br />\n嗚門雖然平時都係傻傻下,但一到重要時間就擺出男子應有態度面對<br />\n由人面人憎咩都唔識死o靚仔,到自來也死再到忍界大戰,每件事都能夠睇得出嗚門ge改變同成長"}]}